Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.39,0:00:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「Yellow Radio」！？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.54,0:00:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黃之王 為什麼會在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.72,0:00:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王？ 那個就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,率領黃之軍團的 等級9的「超頻連線者」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(858,655)}<Burst Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.93,0:00:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.45,0:00:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是你所設計的嗎 「Yellow Radio」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.31,0:00:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀哦呀 你好呀 紅之王
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.97,0:00:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是巧遇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.90,0:00:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你胡說什麼 明明是你埋伏在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.06,0:00:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現實裡1秒這裡就是17分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.50,0:00:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事先計畫好的話不可能會遇到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.21,0:00:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是過分的說法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.02,0:00:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42}我不過是 有部下因為有人違反了不可侵條約而被逼入「點數」全損的境地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.02,0:00:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\pos(975,655)}<Point>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.29,0:01:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想讓紅之軍團的某人負起責任而已哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.00,0:01:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黃之王 偷偷把「災禍之鎧」藏起來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.78,0:01:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後把它交給「Cherry Rook」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.93,0:01:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來把仁子 把「Scarlet Rain」引出來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.89,0:01:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可侵條約中有這麼一條
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.00,0:01:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,軍團的成員由於違反條約的襲擊而被逼入到強制卸載的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該軍團可以從襲擊者的軍團隨意選擇一名 給予相同的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.62,0:01:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到那個隨意的一名居然會是紅之王 「Scarlet Rain」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.37,0:01:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是為了狩獵讓自己達成等級10所需的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.83,0:01:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,代價的其中之一
Comment: 0,0:01:53.06,0:01:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.06,0:01:58.45,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(150,200)}この瞳は 鮮やかに舞う キミしか知覚らない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.70,0:02:06.66,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(150,200)}踏み込んで覚醒ざめる セカイへ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:18.30,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(150,200)}俯き過ぎて小さい 僕だけの景色が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.93,0:02:25.26,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(150,200)}組み立てたジオラマの嘘だと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.51,0:02:31.06,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(150,200)}合わせ辛い視点に 気付いている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.60,0:02:41.21,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(150,200)}駆け出してゆく未来は 美しさを手に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.78,0:02:50.12,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(150,200)}それぞれが翔べる場所を 問い掛けてく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.76,0:02:59.23,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(150,200)}この瞳は 鮮やかに舞う キミしか知覚らない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.41,0:03:04.82,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(150,200)}加速して初めて 往(ゆ)ける僕は僕の先へ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:10.52,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(150,200)}もっと昂く もっと強く キミに届きたい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:18.13,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(150,200)}踏み込んで覚醒ざめる chasin' the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.06,0:01:58.45,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(150,200)}唯有你知從我的雙眸迸發出的絢麗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.70,0:02:06.66,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(150,200)}闖進這個世界中覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:18.30,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(150,200)}俯瞰那專屬於我的渺小世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.93,0:02:25.26,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(150,200)}但卻被捏造的假象
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.51,0:02:31.06,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(150,200)}失焦了我的雙眼 方然覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.60,0:02:41.21,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(150,200)}衝刺而來的未來 將美好緊握手中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.78,0:02:50.12,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(150,200)}追尋各自飛翔的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.76,0:02:59.23,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(150,200)}唯有你知從我的雙眸迸發出的絢麗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.41,0:03:04.82,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(150,200)}開始加速向著我的前方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:10.52,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(150,200)}想要更加激昂 更加強大地傳達於你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:18.13,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(150,200)}闖進這個世界中覺醒 chasin' the world
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.82,0:03:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎 是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.04,0:03:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您能理解真是再好不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 條約中應該也這麼寫了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管可以隨意選擇一名復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.91,0:03:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「軍團長」親自制裁了違反者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.91,0:03:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(477,655)}<Legion Master>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使其「點數」全損的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(560,655)}<Point>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.34,0:03:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不再有那個權利了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.27,0:03:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實如此 但是我有聽說到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.06,0:03:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您前幾天打算這麼做時居然失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要再挑戰一次的話請隨意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.47,0:03:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是那個違反者什麼時候會出現呢 什麼時候能打倒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.47,0:04:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果現在無法立刻處理的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.39,0:04:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能用您來抵債了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.78,0:04:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是陷阱 仁子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.43,0:04:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暫時先「登出」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.43,0:04:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(680,655)}<Logout>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.83,0:04:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後再等下次機會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.44,0:04:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在無限制中立戰場的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.92,0:04:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即時「登出」是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.92,0:04:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(578,655)}<Logout>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣的 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要從這裡離開的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.47,0:04:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須要去到配置在各處的「脫離點」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.47,0:04:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(858,655)}<Leave Point>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣的系統
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 距離那個「脫離點」…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(741,655)}<Leave Point>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.92,0:04:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使是距離這裡最近的那一個 也是池袋站或者「陽光城」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.92,0:04:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(1049,655)}<Sunshine City>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何 必須都要戰鬥一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 Radio那傢伙也有失算
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.66,0:04:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失算？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.76,0:04:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那傢伙大概為了狩獵我一個人而聚集了那麼多人數
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.77,0:04:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但現在 這裡有另外一個王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.83,0:04:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情況就是如此 「Black Lotus」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.55,0:04:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在正要開幕的愉快嘉年華
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:05:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您會待在一邊參觀的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.64,0:05:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了 「Yellow Radio」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我必須要按你所計畫的那樣行動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.25,0:05:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀哦呀 真是聽不明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難得我還準備了這樣的禮物了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.49,0:05:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.25,0:05:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上一代的紅之王 「Red Rider」？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上一代的王？
Comment: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.71,0:05:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就是一直為了這個無聊的目的而戰鬥至今嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,互相憎恨 互相奪取 互相殺戮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.77,0:05:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們各自率領「軍團」戰鬥至今
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.77,0:05:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(680,655)}<Legion>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕不是因為我們互相是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.38,0:05:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們互相都是競爭對手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.42,0:05:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜歡你的戰鬥方法 Lotus
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使某一天和你在現實世界相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.36,0:05:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也會成為好朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我很想成為你的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不想和你進行這種即死的殺戮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.83,0:06:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是一樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.35,0:06:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.31,0:06:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的可不能聽過就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.78,0:06:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊 不是那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.83,0:06:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頭疼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.76,0:06:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 正如你所說的一樣 Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.66,0:06:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也喜歡你 當然 是尊敬的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.04,0:06:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.08,0:06:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.05,0:06:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.49,0:06:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要生氣嘛 是代替握手嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「死亡擁抱」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(640,655)}<Death by Embracing>
Comment: 0,0:06:47.43,0:06:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.30,0:07:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真令人懷念呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住…住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手 住手 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.86,0:07:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學…學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.65,0:07:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,春…春雪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.42,0:07:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.95,0:07:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學姐 學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「零化現象」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(640,655)}<Zero Fill>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lotus 你居然那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.59,0:07:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道她還沒放下那次背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.21,0:07:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 用那種覺悟居然就以等級10為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令人捧腹大笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊準備
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 強化外…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.67,0:07:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 紅之王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.76,0:08:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果展開武器的話 你就無法移動了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在應該撤退到「陽光城」的「脫離點」去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(640,655)}<Sunshine City>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(880,655)}<Leave Point>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.43,0:08:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小春 我來做盾牌 吾王就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.72,0:08:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…那樣的話你就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打倒紅之王後 他們肯定會打吾王的主意的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯有這件事不能讓他們得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.57,0:08:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊開始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.15,0:08:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小春 小心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.19,0:08:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無限制戰場裡的痛覺是2倍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.27,0:08:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿拓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.25,0:08:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小春 跑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:09:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點 還差一點就能到達環形坑的邊緣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.88,0:09:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡開始 就抱起學姐和仁子 一口氣…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無謂的掙扎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.54,0:09:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「愚人的旋轉木馬」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.54,0:09:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(640,655)}<Silly Go-Round>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.83,0:09:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.35,0:09:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,場景在…旋轉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.06,0:09:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對 只是看上去在旋轉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把眼睛閉起來快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.86,0:09:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿拓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我欠你的 這點程度根本還不了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.07,0:09:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 沒有那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.33,0:09:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要我說幾次才能明白啊 阿拓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.50,0:09:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿拓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.92,0:09:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只有頭腦好這點我撤回 「Cyan Pile」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.13,0:10:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有30秒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有30秒 Radio的必殺技就會消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.80,0:10:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.08,0:10:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然聽說幹的相當不錯 但似乎只是自滿於硬度而已啊 「Cyan Pile」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.71,0:10:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被撕開來之前給我記住 打倒你的是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.59,0:10:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對笨蛋的名字…沒有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.53,0:10:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「雷霆快槍」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.53,0:10:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(640,655)}<Lightning Cyan Spike>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.12,0:10:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿拓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.35,0:10:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後…就交給你了 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.56,0:10:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「飛針四射」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.56,0:10:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(640,655)}<Splash Stinger>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿拓 你果然很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.03,0:10:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我自豪的摯友
Comment: 0,0:10:56.31,0:11:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.06,0:11:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿拓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.58,0:11:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學姐 學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑雪公主學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會什麼不站起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.89,0:11:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的 「Silver Crow」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.23,0:11:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在應該從她的腦中輸出的「虛擬角色」的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.23,0:11:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(824,655)}<Avatar>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.24,0:11:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是0了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有鬥志的「超頻連線者」是無法驅動「對戰虛擬角色」的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(457,655)}<Burst Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(963,655)}<Duel Avatar>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.45,0:11:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有直面天命般的心之傷的力量的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就連站起來都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.92,0:11:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是「Brain Burst」這個遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.36,0:11:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心之傷…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帶著Lotus逃吧 「Silver Crow」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 雖然捨棄了「Cyan Pile」而賺到了一點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:11:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是能在這種情況下能逃命的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.02,0:12:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.96,0:12:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭扔下夥伴自己逃命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夥伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你真是個一條經的笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.99,0:12:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨你喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「Yellow Radio」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.30,0:12:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那個耗盡了你的必殺技槽了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次輪到這邊來回報你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘記了啊 被我打倒了的話 你也是永久退場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.48,0:12:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 強化外裝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.39,0:12:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 「Silver Crow」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.29,0:12:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠近屁股的那些接近型對手就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.43,0:12:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我被幹掉了的話 就帶著Lotus飛走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.03,0:12:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仁子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.47,0:12:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們怕什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:12:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西只不過是個固定炮臺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要靠近了就只是個大鐵塊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不需要感到恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.35,0:13:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我上
Comment: 0,0:13:05.19,0:13:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們的對手是紅之王這點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來讓你們好好體會一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.66,0:13:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好…好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.45,0:13:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.07,0:13:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,礙事啊 雜魚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「磁力波」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(640,655)}<Magnetron Wave>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.22,0:13:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為是金屬嘛 吸得真緊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.51,0:14:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨…笨蛋 我的必殺技只有13秒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.57,0:14:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿 鑽啊鑽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.32,0:14:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與金屬色的打擊特化者進入近接戰的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.79,0:14:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卸掉攻擊 利用其威力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.26,0:14:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按你的反應速度的話 是辦的到的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.45,0:14:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你個小弱兵還挺行的嘛 「Silver Crow」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那真是多謝誇獎了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 是干擾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.08,0:15:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快去找出來 Crow
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是黃色軍團的某人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.35,0:15:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.61,0:15:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「電擊療法」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.61,0:15:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(640,655)}<Electri Therapy>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暫時在那躺一會吧 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.41,0:15:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直到紅之王全身都被剝光為止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.03,0:15:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.11,0:15:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,何等丟臉 何等滑稽的姿態啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全喪失王的尊嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.28,0:15:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終究只是順勢上位的紅和叛徒的黑嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.46,0:15:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好囉 紅之王也就是這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小的們 把皮全部剝掉 把她拖出來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.34,0:16:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學…學姐 學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能接受這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.96,0:16:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種結束方式 是你所期望的結局嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑之王 對你而言 加速是什麼 「Brain Burst」是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那達到前無古人的等級10的野望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.74,0:16:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廉價到僅用一個男人的回憶就能換得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.31,0:16:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要在那裡睡到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.25,0:16:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你應該斬斷一切障礙 揮去一切障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.12,0:16:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直奮戰到最後一人為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.58,0:16:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「Black Lotus」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.81,0:17:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學…姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.19,0:17:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,春雪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.42,0:17:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按照你的說法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和Rider簡直像是戀人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.19,0:17:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斷然不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我應該有說過 你是第一個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.97,0:17:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有 你別一直躺在地上 試試把一隻手插進地面上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 土地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後你自己能處理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去稍微照顧一下小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.06,0:17:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:17:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.15,0:18:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我而言 擒拿技基本是無效的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然與你們無怨無仇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 與我戰鬥的人 必然會品嚐到肢體殘缺的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且是在2倍痛覺的這個戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在可別說不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.34,0:18:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下 我現在正在充電
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.26,0:18:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.28,0:18:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼到現在才出現來妨礙我 「Black Lotus」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.34,0:18:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你忘記了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.91,0:18:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的友人被你背叛 被你斬下頭顱的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:18:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 他現在在哪裡幹些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法再次回歸的加速世界這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與造成其原因的某人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他有沒有想起這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.56,0:19:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的話是不會忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.67,0:19:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,普通的對戰暫且不論
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那種趁人不備啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.55,0:19:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.64,0:19:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你誤會了一點 「Yellow Radio」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.98,0:19:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 哪一點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.58,0:19:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我而言 你的頭顱的重量與「Red Rider」的是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.80,0:19:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有再告訴你一點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.03,0:19:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.10,0:19:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從第一次與你見面時就看你不爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.37,0:19:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raid 剩下武裝的裝載完成了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.36,0:19:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crow 保護她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.73,0:19:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我再清淨一會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.66,0:19:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crow 干擾的發信源在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.17,0:20:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和那個時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.59,0:20:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不一樣了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.03,0:20:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仁子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.45,0:20:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.02,0:20:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lotus！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:20:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:20:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是等級9之間的戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.31,0:21:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.36,0:21:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是加速世界開始以來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.54,0:21:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次發生等級9之間的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.08,0:21:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.08,0:21:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雙方的必殺技槽 差不多要滿了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正戲現在正要開始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.94,0:21:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lotus的必殺技 恐怕是直接攻擊系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.78,0:21:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與此相對 Radio大概是幻覺系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.61,0:21:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在Radio的必殺技發動前 Lotus的一擊能不能打的到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.66,0:21:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是分水嶺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.33,0:21:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「死亡穿刺」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.33,0:21:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(640,655)}<Death by Piercing>
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.37,0:21:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「無意義的命運車」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.37,0:21:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(640,655)}<Futile Fortune Wheel>
Comment: 0,0:22:12.07,0:22:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.07,0:22:15.42,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}We are tossed by the waves of pain and tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.42,0:22:19.25,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}I'm tossed into the fray tossed by various fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.25,0:22:20.88,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}Wake up your brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.93,0:22:22.88,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}Flashed in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.00,0:22:25.38,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}It's a 「Burst」 of sensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.38,0:22:31.66,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}「諦め」がくれた 安楽 沈滞の世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.72,0:22:34.66,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}いつからだっただろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.73,0:22:37.75,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}ふいに輝き始めた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.78,0:22:41.10,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}-変わらずにいてと願うこと-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.10,0:22:44.76,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}-変わりゆく時に生きる僕ら-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.82,0:22:47.93,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}本当の声を…言い得ぬ夢を…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.93,0:22:50.22,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}君と繋がった空へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.32,0:22:52.20,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}響かせて！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.72,0:22:56.16,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}もっと強く…この両手で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.28,0:22:59.49,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}涙全て振り払えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.58,0:23:02.81,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}「今度こそは…」 つぶやく今と
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.91,0:23:06.07,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}傷さえも無駄にしない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.14,0:23:09.37,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}もっと早く…君のもとへ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.45,0:23:12.59,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}たとえ羽が千切れようとも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.67,0:23:15.92,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}歪む世界 走り抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.98,0:23:19.16,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}感覚のその向うへ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.26,0:23:24.76,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}「真実」と 加速してく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.07,0:22:15.42,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}我們遭受淚水與傷痛煩心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.42,0:22:19.25,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}而我被置身於那亂於無數未來的競爭之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.25,0:22:20.88,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}將自身覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.93,0:22:22.88,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}閃現於高空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.00,0:22:25.38,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}這就是「加速」快感
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.38,0:22:31.66,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}「放棄」帶來的安樂停滯世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.72,0:22:34.66,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}何時悄然而至的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.73,0:22:37.75,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}恍然間光輝耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.78,0:22:41.10,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}祈求永恆無變
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.10,0:22:44.76,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}我們卻生活在幻化無常的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.82,0:22:47.93,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}搭載著吐露的真聲與難以言說的夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.93,0:22:50.22,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}與你一同展翅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.32,0:22:52.20,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}讓聲音迴蕩在天際！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.72,0:22:56.16,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}更加的堅強…用雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.28,0:22:59.49,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}將淚水全部抹去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.58,0:23:02.81,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}喃喃而道「下次一定…」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.91,0:23:06.07,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}不會讓傷痛僅僅成為過往
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.14,0:23:09.37,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}更加快速地…到達你的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.45,0:23:12.59,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}即使羽翼已支離破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.67,0:23:15.92,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}仍會奔跑在這個扭曲的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.98,0:23:19.16,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}依循著感覺的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.26,0:23:24.76,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}與「真實」一同加速
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.90,0:23:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}下一話 Absolution;容赦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.61,0:23:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}於是決斷之時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.39,0:23:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}愛之罪該饒恕嗎
